moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過話說搵倉鼠資料真係好小見關於生仔之後既事<br />\n靜係教你點樣養,俾咩佢食<br />\n冇乜資訊係教人唔好男女一齊養或者生左之後點處理<br />\n亦都好小會介紹佢本身習性<br />\n搞到好多人唔知頭唔知路塞哂入籠俾野佢食就話好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca593468de91eb51db5474f7b8666383ca42fb1","tid":1168942,"uid":92340,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"俾你知道將來又要住劏房，得啲死人乾糧食，成世人活動空間得一呎唔夠，你都會食啦，窮人倉鼠學咩人生仔"},{"pid":"40eb173e29b4a8e75c071be374fa96438157c1f8","tid":1168942,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ca593468de91eb51db5474f7b8666383ca42fb1","tid":1168942,"uid":92340,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"俾你知道將來又要住劏房，得啲死人乾糧食，成世人活動空間得一呎唔夠，你都會食啦，窮人倉鼠學咩人生仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真理"},{"pid":"6fb8bef9cfa96b1e691df9d4c21ad4081eb037e3","tid":1168942,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"34afdfef850597c3b3613a0c10d020c2ab3828b8","tid":1168942,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"好似話佢受驚會為咗保護BB食返佢落肚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"有熟悉倉鼠習性者解釋，倉鼠媽媽若覺得BB有危險會將BB吃掉，鼠媽媽情緒太緊張或遭人打擾亦有吃兒可能，至於雄性倉鼠則對鼠BB無甚感情，吃兒不出為奇，因此應分開飼養。"},{"pid":"73800bfdd36e77c9a9c832127113b902f4537821","tid":1168942,"uid":78574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fb8bef9cfa96b1e691df9d4c21ad4081eb037e3","tid":1168942,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"34afdfef850597c3b3613a0c10d020c2ab3828b8","tid":1168942,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"rep